## Health
GET {{baseUrlGig}}/health

### Update Settings me user
PATCH {{baseUrlGig}}/gig/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "buyer":{
  "badgesAwarded": "<badges>",
  "businessAddress": "business_address>",
  "businessName": "<business_name>",
  "businessRegistrationNumber": "<business_registration_number>",
  "businessRole": "<business_role>",
  "representativeId": "representative_id",
  "socialNetworkUrl": "https://example.com",
  "videoUrl": "https://example.com"
  },

  "worker":{
  "feedbackSummary": "<feedback_summary>",
  "socialNetworkUrl": "https://example.com",
  "tags": "<tags>"
  }
}

### Register gig work
POST {{baseUrlGig}}/gig/work
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "additionalInstructions": "Please bring your own tools.",
  "address": "123 Main St, Anytown, USA",
  "description": "Looking for a skilled Bartender.",
  "endDate": "2025-07-23",
  "latitude": 51.5,
  "longitude": 0.0,
  "paymentPerHour": 25,
  "skills": ["Bartender"],
  "startDate": "2025-07-20",
  "title": "Bartender"
}

### Register Gig Work Team
POST {{baseUrlGig}}/gig/work-team
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endDateOffer": "2025-07-22",
  "gigWorkId": 1,
  "skillId": 2,
  "totalPayment": 15
}